00:21.888 --> 00:22.887
Yes!

00:22.887 --> 00:23.886
Edgar, you take care of Kabe!

00:23.886 --> 00:24.885
Roger!

00:24.885 --> 00:30.879
Thank you, Slard-Seld!

00:38.871 --> 00:42.867
It's the Magical Wind Waker! If we don't defeat it, we won't be able to use Kuroki's magic!

00:42.867 --> 00:44.865
If you hide, we'll catch you!

00:44.865 --> 00:45.864
Hey!

00:45.864 --> 00:47.862
