01:08.841 --> 01:10.839
You don't remember?

01:10.839 --> 01:15.834
Yeah, it's different from when I was holding him in my arms.

01:15.834 --> 01:20.829
He's scary, but he's become stronger because he's yearning for that strength.

01:20.829 --> 01:22.827
This is...

01:22.827 --> 01:24.825
It's about the old man!

01:24.825 --> 01:27.822
He's being respected so much!

01:27.822 --> 01:29.820
Wait!

01:29.820 --> 01:31.818
His strength is real.

01:33.816 --> 01:36.813
What's with that?

01:36.813 --> 01:39.810
Gigant Hunter, Doldor Rexdor!

01:39.810 --> 01:47.802
I'm sorry.

01:47.802 --> 01:49.800
I was wrong.

01:49.800 --> 01:51.798
I'm sorry, old man.

01:51.798 --> 01:58.791
I'm going to the bathroom.

01:58.791 --> 02:02.787
You two can watch over him.

02:04.785 --> 02:07.782
I can't lose to the Black Knight.

02:07.782 --> 02:10.779
Yeah, the Black Knight is amazing, too.

02:10.779 --> 02:12.777
He's a weird guy.

02:12.777 --> 02:14.775
Old man!

02:14.775 --> 02:16.773
Hey, old man!

02:16.773 --> 02:17.772
I'm begging you!

02:17.772 --> 02:18.771
That's enough!

02:18.771 --> 02:21.768
Let me see him first!

02:21.768 --> 02:22.767
Old man!

02:22.767 --> 02:24.765
I'm sorry, old man.

02:24.765 --> 02:25.764
I'm sorry.

02:25.764 --> 02:30.759
"The Black Knight"

04:10.858 --> 04:12.437
He's not coming out.

04:12.437 --> 04:14.275
Will he be okay?

04:14.275 --> 04:16.932
I believe in your strength.

04:16.932 --> 04:18.930
You'll get better.

04:18.930 --> 04:20.349
You're right.

04:20.349 --> 04:23.226
So let's wait while watching the video.

04:23.226 --> 04:24.764
Okay!

04:24.764 --> 04:26.762
Hurry! Let's continue!

04:26.762 --> 04:27.761
You...

04:27.761 --> 04:37.751
Um...

04:38.850 --> 04:42.467
It's the order of wind, fire, and ice.

04:42.467 --> 04:52.457
Old man!

04:55.853 --> 04:57.352
He's alive!

04:57.352 --> 04:58.351
You!

04:58.351 --> 05:03.885
- Old man! - That must hurt!

05:03.885 --> 05:13.875
"The

05:16.593 --> 05:17.791
Safe"

